'Yan majalisar dokokin Wales sun damu da hotunan Muppets
Akwai rashin jituwa tsakanin wasu 'yan majalisa game da shawarar cewa ya kamata a canza taken matsayinsa zuwa MWP (Majalisar Majalisar Welsh).
Dalilin haka shi ne, ana shirin sauya sunan majalisa zuwa majalisar dokokin Wales.
Dukkanin 'yan siyasa masu son siyasa suna damuwa da cewa za a yi musu ba'a.
Wani AM na ma'aikata ya ce kungiyarsa na damuwa da cewa ba za a haɗa shi da Twp da Pwp ba.
Ga masu karatu da ke zaune a waje da Wales: a cikin Welsh, twp yana nufin wawa kuma pwp yana nufin datti.
Wani mai ba da labari na Pled AM ya ce duk kungiyar "ba ta da farin ciki" kuma ta ba da shawarar wasu zaɓuɓɓuka.
Wata jam'iyyar siyasa ta Welsh ta ce kungiyarta "mai ra'ayin mazan jiya" ce game da canjin sunan, amma ta lura cewa za a iya yin amfani da MWP ta hanyar yin magana da kalmomi.
A wannan yanayin, ana furta harafin w a cikin Welsh kamar yadda ake furta harafin u a cikin Yorkshire Turanci.
A halin yanzu, Hukumar Majalisar Dokoki, wacce ke shirya dokar game da canjin sunan, ta ce: "Dokar karshe ta kowane mai bayani game da abin da ake kira 'yan majalisar dokoki, tabbas zai zama batun su ga 'yan majalisa".
A cewar Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017, Majalisar Wakilai tana da ikon canza sunanta.
A watan Yuni, hukumar ta sanar da sakamakon shawarwarin jama'a kan shawarwarin da suka sami goyon baya sosai don canza sunan majalisa zuwa majalisar dokokin Wales.
Game da taken AM, Hukumar ta goyi bayan 'yan majalisa na Welsh ko WMP, amma mafi yawan goyon baya a cikin shawarwarin jama'a shine zaɓin MWP.
A bayyane yake, AM tana ba da shawarar wasu zaɓuɓɓuka da yawa, amma yana da matukar wahala ga mai gudanarwa Elin Jones don samun yarjejeniya, tana fatan gabatar da tsarin doka don canji a cikin 'yan makonni.
Dokar da ake tsarawa don canje -canje za ta kuma haɗa da wasu canje -canje a cikin hanyoyin aiki a cikin Majalisar, gami da ƙa'idodin rashin cancantar AM da tsarin kwamitin.
A lokacin da ake muhawara game da yin doka, AM za ta sami kuri 'a ta ƙarshe a kan abin da za a kira su.
