Sama da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka halarci shari'ar da aka yi a ranar Alhamis a Kotun Koli, a kan wata mata da ta zargi Brett Cavanough da laifin cin zarafin mata a shekarun 1980s, Christine Blasey Ford, wanda aka nuna a tashoshin talabijin shida.
A halin yanzu, an kuma ga cikas a siyasa, inda masu watsa shirye-shirye suka dakatar da shirin yau da kullun na Jumma'a na Last-Minute Twist: An Agreement Engineered by Arizona Sen. An shigar da karar ne bayan Jeff Flake na FBI ya yi bincike na mako guda kan zargin.
