ABC ta kasance ta biyu a cikin masu kallo miliyan 3. 26.
An samu masu kallo miliyan 3.1 a CBS, miliyan 2.94 a NBC, miliyan 2.89 a MSNBC da miliyan 2.52 a CNN, Nielsen ya ruwaito.
