An harbe Wade Sims: 'Yan sanda sun tsare wani mutum mai suna Dayton Simpson a matsayin wanda ake zargi da mutuwar dan wasan LSU
'Yan sanda sun tsare wani mutum da ake zargi da harbi da kisan Wade Sims, dan wasan kwando na LSU mai shekara 20.
'Yan sanda sun ce an kama Dighton Simpson, mai shekara 20, kuma an tsare shi a kurkuku saboda laifin kisan kai na biyu.
Jami'ai sun fitar da bidiyon gamuwa tsakanin Sims da Simpson, kuma 'yan sanda sun ce Sims ya rasa tabarau a lokacin gamuwa.
'Yan sanda sun karɓi tabarau daga wurin da aka yi aukuwar lamarin kuma sun ce DNA ta kasance ta Simpson, a cewar rahoton WAFB da ke da alaƙa da CBS.
Da aka yi wa Simpson tambayoyi, 'yan sanda sun bayyana cewa ya harbe Wade har ya mutu.
Rahoton lauya ya nuna cewa an ba shi dala 350,000 don wannan.
Rahoton farko da ofishin mai binciken wadanda suka mutu a yankin East Baton Rouge ya fitar a ranar Juma'a ya ce harbin da aka yi wa wuyansa ne ya yi sanadin mutuwar.
Ma'aikatar ta ba da wannan daraja ga 'yan sanda na jihar Louisiana Fugitive Task Force, State Police Crime Lab, 'yan sanda na Jami'ar Kudancin, da kuma mutanen yankin da suka ba da haɗin kai a cikin binciken don tsare su.
Daraktan wasannin motsa jiki na LSU Joe Alleva ya gode wa dokar da ta shafi yankin saboda "aikinta da neman adalci".
Sims yana da shekara 20.
Ya kasance mai tsayi 6ft 6in, ya girma a Baton Rouge, inda mahaifinsa Wayne, wanda ya buga wasan kwando a LSU, yake zaune.
Ya samu maki 5.6 da rebounds 2.6 a wasan bara.
Kocin kwando na LSU Will Wade ya bayyana a safiyar ranar Juma'a cewa kungiyar ta "karye" kuma "ta yi bakin ciki" saboda mutuwar Wade.
Wade ya ce, "A koyaushe za a damu da wanda zai maye gurbinsa".
