A cikin waɗannan ɗalibai, kashi 68 cikin ɗari sun sami mafi girman maki A a harsunan waje.
Bayanai da aka tattara daga makarantun membobin SCIS 74 sun nuna cewa kashi 72 cikin ɗari na ɗaliban sun sami mafi girman darajar A a cikin harshen Mandarin, yayin da kashi 72 cikin ɗari na ɗaliban suka sami A a cikin harshen Jamusanci, kashi 69 cikin ɗari na ɗaliban a cikin harshen Faransanci, da kuma kashi 63 cikin ɗari na ɗaliban da suka sami A a cikin harshen Sifaniyanci.
Wannan ya nuna cewa makarantun masu zaman kansu a Scotland suna aiki tare a harsunan waje don ba yara da matasa ƙwarewar da za su buƙaci a nan gaba.
