A cikin Wheeling, West Virginia, shugaban kasa Donald Trump ya yi gangami mai yawa a daren yau don yakin neman zabe.
A mako mai zuwa, Trump ya shirya wasu gangami guda biyar, da suka hada da Tennessee da Mississippi, da kuma wasu wurare masu kyau.
Tare da dakatar da kuri'un da aka tsara a zabensa don nadin mukamin Kotun Koli, Trump na da niyyar neman taimako don zaben tsakiyar lokaci mai zuwa saboda akwai barazanar cewa 'yan Republican za su fice daga ikon majalisa a lokacin da aka ƙidaya kuri'un a watan Nuwamba.
Yaushe ne taron Trump zai gudana a yammacin Virginia kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon sa ta yanar gizo?
An shirya lokacin taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia don yau da dare Asabar, Satumba 29, 2018 da karfe 7 na yamma ET.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia ta hanyar YouTube.
Trump na iya yin jawabi a sauraron wannan makon don dan takarar Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka dakatar da tabbatar da kuri'ar majalisar dattijai da ake tsammani na mako guda yayin binciken FIT saboda zargin cin zarafin jima'i da aka yi wa Kavanaugh.
Amma babban burin wannan yanayi na zanga -zanga shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican su fuskanci zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A cewar Reuters, kamar yadda Shugaba Trump ya bayyana a lokacin yakin, "Masu aikin sa kai da magoya baya a mako mai zuwa suna da nufin karfafa gwiwa a matsayin kokarin Republican na karewa da kara yawan rinjaye a majalisar dattijai da na wakilai".
A cewar Reuters, mai magana da yawun da aka cire daga yakin neman zaben Trump ya ce, "Sarrafa majalisar dokoki ya zama muhimmiyar mahimmancin ajandarmu cewa shugaban zai ziyarci jihohin da muke da babban yakin neman zabe".
A cewar West Virginia Metro News, gangamin da aka shirya a gidan wasan Wesbank Arena a Wheeling, zai iya jan hankalin magoya bayan Ohio da Pennsylvania zuwa kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh.
A ranar Asabar ne dai Trump zai ziyarci jihar West Virginia a karo na biyu a cikin watan da ya gabata, inda ya samu kashi 40 cikin 100 na kuri'un da aka kada a 2016.
Trump ya zo ne don taimakawa dan takarar da ya fi tsayi a zaben Sanata na Jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia, Patrick Morris.
A cewar Reuters, wani masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, Simon Hayder, ya ce, "Idan shugaban kasa ya yi kokarin ganin ya samu nasara a zaben, ba alama ce mai kyau ba a gare shi".
