A wannan Asabar, New York za ta karbi bakuncin bikin Global Citizen Festival, wani biki na shekara-shekara wanda ke nuna manyan taurari masu tasiri, kuma suna da manufa mai tasiri; kawar da talauci a duniya.
Yanzu a shekara ta bakwai, bikin Global Citizen Festival zai tara dubban mutane a babban filin shakatawa na Central Park don jin daɗin masu fasaha kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes, amma kuma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin burin shirin na kawar da matsanancin talauci nan da shekarar 2030.
An fara bikin a shekarar 2012, bikin na Global Citizen wani ci gaba ne na kungiyar bada tallafi ta kasa da kasa, Global Poverty Project, wadda ke fatan kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke yaki da talauci.
Don samun tikiti kyauta don taron (sai dai idan kuna son biyan tikitin VIP), masu halartar wasan kwaikwayon dole ne su zama masu sa kai don taimakawa wajen wayar da kan jama'a game da burin su na kawar da talauci, su cika ayyuka da yawa kamar imel, kiran waya ga wani shugaban duniya, ko wasu hanyoyi masu ma'ana.
Amma yaya 'yan ƙasa na duniya suka yi nasara a cikin shekaru 12 da suka gabata wajen cimma burinsu?
Shin ra'ayin bayar da kyauta ta kyauta ta kyauta hanya ce mai kyau ta shawo kan mutane su yi kira zuwa aiki, ko kuma wani abu ne da ake kira "clectivism" - mutane suna jin kamar suna kawo canji ta hanyar sanya hannu kan takarda kan layi ko aika tweet?
Tun daga 2011, Global Citizen ya ce ya rubuta sama da "aiki" miliyan 19 daga magoya bayansa, yana ci gaba da kokarin cimma manufofi daban-daban.
