Daley ta auri Oscar wanda ya girme ta da shekara 20, amma ta ce bambancin shekaru bai taba zama matsala ba.
"Lokacin da kake fuskantar abubuwa da yawa a wannan lokacin" - ya halarci gasar Olympics ta farko yana ɗan shekara 14 kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu daga ciwon daji shekaru uku bayan haka - ya ce yana da wuya a sami wani ɗan'uwa da ya fuskanci irin wannan yanayi a wannan lokacin.
A watan Yuni ma'auratan sun zama iyayen wani yaro mai suna Robert Ray Black-Daley, kuma Daley ya ce "dukkan halinsa" ya canza.
"Idan ka tambaye ni a bara, duk abin da zai kasance game da 'Ina bukatar lashe lambar zinare,'" in ji shi.
