Ya kamata a ce jirgin ya shiga cikin Sojojin Ruwa a shekarar 2014, amma matsalolin da ke tattare da shi bayan bayarwa sun shafi makomar wannan babban shiri.
Sojojin ruwa sun ba da umarnin jiragen ruwa hudu na Baden-Württemberg a cikin 2007 don maye gurbin jiragen ruwa na Bremen da suka lalace.
An fahimci cewa za su samar da wasu fasahohin ɓoyewa kamar ƙananan radar, infrared da kuma ɓoyayyen sauti tare da tarin manyan bindigogi, anti-aircraft da anti-ship missiles.
Sauran mahimman fasali sun haɗa da tsawon lokacin kulawa - yana yiwuwa a tura sabbin jiragen ruwa na zamani har zuwa shekaru biyu daga tashoshin jiragen ruwa na cikin gida.
Duk da haka, jinkirin da ake ci gaba da yi yana nufin cewa manyan jiragen ruwa - wanda zai ba Jamus damar yin amfani da wutar lantarki a kasashen waje - za su zama marasa amfani a lokacin da za su shiga sabis, in ji Die Zeine.
An yi ta fama da mummunan jirgin yakin F125 a bara, lokacin da rundunar sojan ruwan Jamus ta ki amincewa da shi kuma ta mayar da shi zuwa gidan jirgin ruwa na Blohm da Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da rundunar sojan ruwa ta dawo da jirgin ruwa ga mai kera shi bayan an kawo shi.
Mutane kalilan ne suka san dalilan janyewar, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ambaci wasu "kurakurai na software da kayan aiki" da suka sa jirgin ya zama mara amfani yayin da aka tura shi yaƙi.
Rashin software ya kasance mai mahimmanci musamman saboda jiragen ruwa na Baden-Württemberg za su kasance da ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa na kimanin 120 - kawai rabin yawan ma'aikatan tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
Bugu da ƙari, an kuma gano cewa jirgin yana da nauyin nauyi wanda ya rage aikinsa kuma ya iyakance ikon Navy don ƙara haɓaka na gaba.
Rhineland - Puffals mai nauyin tan 7,000 ya ninka nauyin jirgi iri ɗaya da Jamus ta yi amfani da shi a Yaƙin Duniya na Biyu.
Baya ga kayan aikin da suka lalace, farashin farashin aikin gaba ɗaya - gami da horar da ma'aikatan jirgin - yana zama matsala.
An ce ya karu daga farkon € 2.2bn zuwa € 3.1bn ($ 3.6bn).
Matsalar sabon jirgin ruwa, wanda ya zama mahimmanci musamman a cikin hasken gargaɗin kwanan nan, yana lalata ƙarfin jirgin ruwan Jamus.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dokokin Jamus, ya yarda cewa sojojin ruwa suna "karyewa daga jiragen ruwa masu aiki".
Jami'in ya ce batun ya zama mai tsanani a tsawon lokaci, yayin da aka cire tsofaffin jiragen daga aiki, amma ba a samar da wasu ba.
Ya ce babu wani daga cikin jiragen ruwa na Baden-Württemberg da ya isa shiga cikin jirgin ruwa.
