Ronaldo ya yi watsi da zargin fyade yayin da lauyoyi suka kai karar mujallar Jamus
Cristiano Ronaldo ya kira zargin fyade da ake yi masa "labaran karya" kuma ya ce mutane suna amfani da sunansa don "tallafa wa kansu".
Lauyoyinsa za su gurfanar da jaridar Der Spiegel ta Jamus, wacce ta wallafa zargin.
Ana zargin dan wasan gaba na Portugal da Juventus da yin fyade kan wata Ba'amurke mai suna Catherine Mayorga a dakin otal din Las Vegas a shekarar 2009.
A ranar Juma'a, Dre Spiegel ya ruwaito cewa ya biya matar dala 375,000 don ta yi shiru game da lamarin.
Da yake jawabi ga mabiyansa miliyan 142 a cikin bidiyon Instagram Live bayan rahoton da'awar, Ronaldo mai shekara 33 ya kira rahotannin "labaran karya".
"A'a, a'a, a'a, a'a, a'a, ba haka ba ne.
Abin da ya fada a yau, labaran karya ne", in ji mai lashe Ballon d'Or sau biyar a gaban kyamara.
"Suna son su yi shelar kansu da sunana.
Wannan abu ne da ya dace.
Suna son su zama sanannu da sunana, amma wannan wani bangare ne na aikinsu.
"Ni mutum ne mai farin ciki kuma komai yana da kyau", in ji dan wasan yana murmushi.
Lauyoyin Ronaldo suna shirin gurfanar da Der Spiegel a gaban kotu kan zargin da suka yi, a cewar Reuters, da suka kira "ra'ayoyin da ba daidai ba a cikin yankin sirri".
Lauyan Christian Schertz ya ce 'yan wasan za su nemi diyya don lalacewar dabi'a a cikin adadin da ya dace da tsananin cin zarafin, wanda wataƙila shine ɗayan manyan keta haƙƙin mutum a cikin' yan shekarun nan.
An ce an yi wannan abin ne a wata suite a Las Vegas a watan Yuni na shekarar 2009.
Bisa ga takardun da aka shigar a Kotun Gundumar Clark County, Nevada, bayan sun hadu a wani gidan wasan dare, Ronaldo da Mayorca sun koma dakin dan wasan, inda suka yi zargin cewa sun yi mata fyade.
Mai jarida ya yi ikirarin cewa Ronaldo ya durƙusa a kan gwiwoyi bayan abin da ya faru kuma ya gaya masa cewa "kashi 99 cikin 100" "mutum ne mai kyau" wanda "kashi ɗaya" ya ɓata masa rai.
Takardun sun yi iƙirarin cewa Ronaldo ya tabbatar da cewa ma'auratan sun yi jima'i, amma sun yarda da juna.
Maiyorga ta kuma yi ikirarin cewa ta je wurin 'yan sanda kuma ta dauki hotunan raunukanta a asibiti, amma daga baya ta amince da yarjejeniyar waje da kotu saboda ta ji "tsoron ramuwa" kuma tana damuwa game da "rashin mutunci a fili".
Matar mai shekara 34 ta ce yanzu tana kokarin kawo karshen yarjejeniyar ne saboda harin da aka yi mata tun bayan abin da ya faru.
Ronaldo ya kusa komawa Real Madrid daga Manchester United a lokacin da aka yi zargin cewa an kai hari, kuma ya kulla yarjejeniyar kudi miliyan 100 da babbar kungiyar caca ta Italiya a wannan bazarar.
Brexit: Birtaniya za ta yi nadamar rasa masana'antun mota
Sakataren kasuwanci Greg Clark ya ce Birtaniya za ta "daure har abada" idan ta rasa matsayinta na jagora a masana'antar kera motoci bayan Brexit.
Ya ce Toyota UK ta shaida wa BBC cewa za ta dakatar da samar da kayayyaki a masana'antar ta a Barnstone kusa da Derby idan Birtaniya ta bar kungiyar EU.
"Muna bukatar mu yi yarjejeniya", in ji Mr. Clark.
Kamfanin kera motoci na Japan ya ce jinkirin iyaka zai iya shafar ayyukan yi a yayin da ba a cimma yarjejeniyar Brexit ba.
Kamfanin The Barnstone - wanda ke kera Oris da Avenis na Toyota - ya samar da motoci kusan 150,000 a shekarar da ta gabata, 90% daga cikinsu ana fitar da su zuwa sauran EU.
"Ina ganin idan Birtaniya ta fice daga EU a karshen watan Maris, za mu dakatar da samar da kayayyaki a masana'antarmu", in ji Marvin Cook, manajan daraktan Toyota a Barnstone.
Sauran kamfanonin kera motoci na Burtaniya, ciki har da Honda, BMW da Jaguar Land Rover sun nuna fargaba game da barin EU ba tare da yarjejeniya kan yadda cinikin kan iyaka zai yi aiki ba.
Alal misali, BMW ta ce za ta rufe ƙaramin masana'anta a Oxford na wata guda bayan Brexit.
A cewar masana'antun motoci, manyan damuwar suna da alaƙa da haɗarin sarkar samarwa a cikin yanayin rashin yarjejeniyar Brexit.
Layin samar da Toyota yana gudana ne akan "kawai-a-lokaci", tare da sassan motocin da aka yi oda daga masu samar da kayayyaki a duk minti 37 daga duka Burtaniya da Tarayyar Turai.
Idan Birtaniya ta bar EU a ranar 29 ga watan Maris ba tare da wata yarjejeniya ba, za a iya samun cikas a kan iyakar, a cewar masana'antar, wanda zai haifar da jinkiri da karancin kayayyakin gyara.
Kamfanin ya ce ba zai yiwu Toyota ta ci gaba da yin amfani da kayan aiki fiye da rana guda a cikin shuka ta Derbyshire ba, saboda haka za a dakatar da samarwa.
Mr. Clark ya ce shirin Theresa May na masu binciken don dangantakar gaba da EU "an daidaita shi ne don kauce wa waɗannan binciken a kan iyaka".
"Muna bukatar yarjejeniya. Muna son mafi kyawun yarjejeniya da nake ganin ba kawai za ta ba mu damar jin daɗin nasararmu a yanzu ba, amma kuma abin da muke buƙata don samun damar", in ji shi a shirin BBC Radio 4 na yau.
"Ba wai kawai daga Toyota ba amma daga wasu masana'antun da suka tabbatar da cewa ya kamata mu iya ci gaba da kasancewa da cikakkiyar hanyar samar da kayayyaki".
Toyota ba ta iya cewa tsawon lokacin da za a dakatar da samarwa ba, amma a cikin dogon lokaci, ta yi gargadin cewa ƙarin farashin zai rage gasa na masana'antar kuma a ƙarshe ya rasa ayyuka.
Peter Savaleris, wanda ya yi aiki a Barnstone tsawon shekaru 24 kuma shine mai tsara kungiyar United a masana'antar, ya ce membobinsu suna cikin damuwa: "A cikin gogewar da nake da ita, da zarar waɗannan ayyukan sun tafi, ba za su sake dawowa ba.
"Mun samar da tsari mai kyau da kuma tabbatacce ga dangantakarmu ta gaba da Tarayyar Turai", in ji wani kakakin gwamnati.
A cewar fadar White House, ana iya sake jinkirta ganawar Trump da Rosenstein
Fadar White House ta ce a ranar Lahadi cewa za a iya jinkirta babban taron da za a yi da mataimakin lauya na Donald Trump Rod Rosenstein zuwa "wata mako" yayin da ake ci gaba da gwagwarmayar dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh.
Rosenstein ya kula da aikin lauya na musamman Robert Mueller, wanda ke binciken shigar da baki a zaben Rasha, alakar da ke tsakanin mataimakin Trump da Rasha da kuma yiwuwar hana shugaban kasa yin adalci.
Ko Trump zai kori mataimakin babban lauyan kasar ko a'a, da kuma cewa 'yancin Muller yana cikin hadari, ya sanya wasu watanni ana ta yada jita-jita a Washington.
A farkon wannan watan, jaridar New York Times ta ruwaito cewa Rosenstein ya tattauna batun sanya waya don rikodin tattaunawa da Trump da kuma yiwuwar cire shugaban ta hanyar Kwaskwarima ta 25.
Rosenstein ya musanta rahoton.
Amma a ranar Litinin da ta gabata ya je fadar White House a yayin da aka sanar da shi cewa zai yi murabus.
Maimakon haka, an sanar da ganawa da Trump a ranar Alhamis, wanda a lokacin yana Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a New York.
Trump ya ce "ba zai so a cire Rosenstein ba" amma sai aka jinkirta taron don kauce wa rikici daga wannan sauraron na kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattijai, wanda duka Kavanah da matar da ta zarge shi da cin zarafin jima'i, Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, suka shaida.
A ranar Juma'a, Trump ya ba da umarnin FBI ta gudanar da bincike na mako guda kan zargin da ake yi wa Kavanah, wanda hakan ya jinkirta kuri'ar majalisar dattijai gaba daya.
Sakatariyar yada labarai ta Trump, Sarah Sanders, ta bayyana a Fox News a ranar Lahadi.
Da aka tambaye ta game da taron Rosenstein, ta ce: "Ba a sanya kwanan wata ba, zai iya zama a wannan makon, zan iya ganin cewa idan aka duba duk sauran shari'o'in da ke gudana tare da Kotun Koli, za a iya matsawa mako guda.
Amma za mu gani kuma ina son ci gaba da sanar da manema labarai".
Wasu 'yan jarida sun yi ikirarin cewa: Sanders bai yi jawabin manema labarai ba tun ranar 10 ga watan Satumba.
Mai gabatarwa Chris Wallace ya tambaye ni dalilin da ya sa.
Sanders ya ce rashin ba da rahoto ba saboda rashin son "al'ajabi" na 'yan jaridar TV ba, ko da yake ya ce: "Ba na rashin yarda da gaskiyar cewa suna da kyau".
Ta sake ba da shawarar ƙara hulɗa kai tsaye tsakanin Trump da 'yan jarida.
Ya ce, "Shugabannin suna da karin tambayoyin tambayoyi fiye da kowane shugaban kasa", ba tare da ambaton shaidar ba, ya ce: "Mun ga waɗannan lambobin".
Za a ci gaba da gudanar da taron, Sanders ya ce, amma "idan 'yan jarida sun sami damar yin tambayoyi kai tsaye ga shugaban Amurka, zai fi kyau su yi magana da ni.
Muna kokarin yin hakan sosai kuma kun ga mun yi hakan sosai a cikin 'yan makonnin da suka gabata kuma lokacin da zaku iya magana da shugaban Amurka zai maye gurbin taron manema labarai. "
Trump yana amsa tambayoyi a kai a kai yayin barin Fadar White House ko halartar zaman buɗe ido ko taron manema labarai tare da manyan mutane.
Taron manema labarai guda ba safai ake yin su ba.
A wannan makon a New York, shugaban ya nuna rashin kunya da kuma wani lokaci na musamman ga 'yan jarida da ke halarta, watakila ya nuna dalilin da ya sa.
Sakataren Lafiya NHS ya rubuta wa ma'aikatan EU a Scotland game da tsoron Brexit
Sakataren Lafiya ya rubuta wa ma'aikatan EU da ke aiki a NHS na Scotland don nuna godiyar kasar da fatan ci gaba bayan Brexit.
Jean Freeman MSP ta aika da wasika ne kasa da wata shida bayan ficewar Birtaniya daga EU.
Gwamnatin Scotland ta riga ta himmatu don biyan kuɗin aikace -aikacen matsayin zama ga EU citizens da ke aiki a cikin ayyukanta na ƙasa.
A cikin wasikar ta, Miss Freeman ta rubuta: "A lokacin rani, tattaunawar tsakanin Burtaniya da EU ta ci gaba, tana kaiwa ga yanke shawara da ake tsammani a wannan kaka.
Amma gwamnatin Burtaniya ma tana ci gaba da shirye -shiryenta don yiwuwar yanayin rashin yarjejeniya.
Na san wannan lokaci ne mai matukar damuwa a gare ku duka.
Wannan shine dalilin da ya sa na sake maimaita cewa ina daraja gudummawar kowane ma'aikaci, ba tare da la'akari da asalin ƙasarsu ba.
Abokan hulɗa a cikin EU, da kuma bayan, suna kawo ƙwarewa da ƙwarewa masu mahimmanci waɗanda ke ƙarfafawa da haɓaka aikin kiwon lafiya, da kuma amfanin marasa lafiya da al'ummomin da muke bauta wa.
