A lokacin da aka yi wa Christian Abercrombie tiyata bayan da ya ji rauni a kansa
Mike Organ na Tennessee ya ruwaito cewa dan wasan Tennessee State Tigers, Christian Abercrombie, wanda ya sha kashi 31-27 a wasan da suka yi da Vanderbilt Commodores a ranar Asabar, ya yi jinya na gaggawa bayan da ya ji rauni a kai.
Kocin jihar Tennessee Rod Reed ya shaida wa manema labarai cewa raunin ya faru ne jim kadan kafin wasan.
"Ya zo gabar teku da kuma kawai fadi a can", Reed ce.
Masu koyarwa da ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya sun ba Abercrombie oxygen a gefe kafin su sanya shi a kan shimfiɗa kuma su dawo da shi don ƙarin kimantawa.
Wani jami'in jihar Tennessee ya shaida wa Chris Harris na WSMV a Nashville, Tennessee cewa Aberdrombie ya fito daga tiyata a cibiyar likitancin Vanderbilt.
Harris ya ce "Babu wani bayani game da nau'in / iyakar raunin da aka samu ba tukuna" kuma Jihar Tennessee na kokarin gano lokacin da raunin ya faru.
Abercrombie, wanda ke cikin shekara ta biyu a matsayin mai saka riguna, yana cikin kakar wasa ta farko da jihar Tennessee bayan ya koma daga Illinois.
Ya yi jimillar takalman biyar a ranar Asabar kafin ya fita daga wasan, ya kawo jimillar takalmansa na kakar wasa 18.
