An kama babban dan Sarah Palin da laifin cin zarafin mata
An kama Track Palin, babban dan gwamna da mataimakin dan takarar shugaban kasa a jihar Alaska, Sarah Palin, saboda zargin cewa ya kai hari.
An kama Palin, mai shekaru 29 daga Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin tashin hankali na cikin gida, don yin wasa da rahoton tashin hankali na cikin gida da kuma adawa da kama, a cewar rahoton da jihar Alaska ta fitar a ranar Asabar.
A cewar rahoton 'yan sanda, idan wata mace da ta san ta yi kokarin kiran 'yan sanda don bayar da rahoton wani laifin da ake zargi, sai ya karbe ta.
A cewar rahoton KTUU, an mayar da Palin zuwa Maut-Su pretrial facility tare da yanke masa hukuncin dalar Amurka 500 a kan wani jinginar gida.
Rahoton cibiyar sadarwa ya ruwaito cewa ya bayyana a gaban kotu a ranar Asabar, inda ya bayyana kansa "ba mai laifi ba" lokacin da aka tambaye shi don yin jayayya.
Palin ya fuskanci laifuffuka uku na Class A, inda za a iya yanke masa hukuncin kisa har zuwa shekara guda da kuma tara $ 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin Class B, wanda ake yanke masa hukuncin kwana daya a gidan yari da kuma tara dala 2,000.
Wannan ba shine karo na farko da aka shigar da karar Palin ba.
A watan Disambar 2017, an same ta da laifin kai wa mahaifinta Todd Palin hari.
Mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don bayar da rahoton zargin da ake yi.
A yanzu haka, wannan shari'ar tana gaban Kotun Alaska ta Masu Gwaji.
A watan Janairun 2016, an tuhume shi da aikata laifin tashin hankali na cikin gida, hana bayar da rahoto game da tashin hankali na cikin gida da kuma mallakar makami yayin da yake bugu dangane da lamarin.
Budurwarsa ta zarge shi da cewa ya buge shi a fuskarsa.
A shekara ta 2016, wata kungiya ta masu gwagwarmaya ta soki Sarah Palin bayan ta danganta halin tashin hankalin ɗanta da PTSD a Iraki.
