Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun nemi hukuncin kisa ga wanda ake zargi da harin NYC
Masu gabatar da kara a New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Safuolo Sipov, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a birnin New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin kisa da aka saba yankewa a jihar don aikata laifin tarayya tun 1953.
Saipov, 30, ya yi amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don yin amfani da keke a kan hanyar da ke kan hanyar yammacin Manhattan, yana kashe masu tafiya da keke a watan Oktoba.
A cewar sanarwar niyyar neman hukuncin kisa da aka gabatar a gundumar kudu ta New York, don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara dole ne su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya "da gangan" ya kashe mutane takwas da kuma "da gangan" ya ji musu rauni.
Dukkan kasashen biyu suna iya yanke hukuncin kisa, a cewar takardun kotun.
Mako guda bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta yanke wa Saipov hukuncin kisa kan laifuka 22, ciki har da laifuka takwas na kisan kai don taimakawa wajen cin zarafin mutane, wanda ake amfani da shi musamman a shari'ar aikata laifuka da kuma tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci "shirye-shiryen da suka dace da kuma shawarwari", suna mai bayanin yadda Saipov ya aiwatar da shi a cikin "m, mummunan hali da kuma mummunan hali".
"Safulau Habibullavich Sipov ya ji rauni kuma ya lalata abokai da dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleaves Enlor Decatt, Darren Drake, Ariel Allerz, Hernan Ferrucci, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Paguneko", in ji sanarwar da aka yi.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe sun kasance masu yawon bude ido daga Argentina.
Shari'ar da aka yi a kan hukuncin kisa na baya a gundumar kudu ta New York ta shafe shekaru goma.
An samu mai laifin Khalid Brain da laifin kashe wasu masu sayar da miyagun kwayoyi biyu amma daga bisani aka yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
A shekarar 1953 ne aka yanke hukuncin kisa a shari'ar tarayya ta New York ga Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka yanke wa hukuncin kisa shekaru biyu da suka gabata saboda yin tawaye ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War.
An kashe Jonne Rosenberg a kan kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, wani mazaunin Uzbekistan, bai ji wani damuwa ko nadama ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan mamayewar, a cewar takardun kotu.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya shaida wa masu binciken cewa ya ji daɗin duk abin da ya yi.
Saipov ya shaida wa jami'an cewa an tilasta masa kai hari bayan da ya kalli bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa yana ganawa da aikata laifuka.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya kuma nemi a nuna masa tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin sa.
Ya nemi kada ya zama mai laifi don laifin lissafi 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin masu kare jama'a na tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce "bacin rai ne" game da hukuncin mai gabatar da kara.
"Muna ganin cewa shawararmu ta neman hukuncin kisa maimakon karbar hukuncin daurin rai da rai ba tare da yiwuwar samun 'yanci ba zai jinkirta cutar da tunanin mutum na wadannan abubuwan da suka faru ba", in ji Patton.
Kungiyar kare Saipov ta fara kira ga masu gabatar da kara da kada su nemi hukuncin kisa.
