Duk da haka, masana sun ce Beijing na iya yin amfani da shi, yakin cinikayya na Amurka zai iya tallafawa China a cikin dogon lokaci, yana rage dogaro da tattalin arzikin biyu.
"Gaskiyar cewa yanke shawara ta siyasa cikin hanzari a Washington ko Beijing na iya haifar da yanayi wanda zai iya haifar da koma bayan tattalin arziki a kasar, wanda a zahiri ya fi haɗari fiye da yadda masu kallo suka gani a baya", in ji Abigail Grace, wata mai bincike da ke mai da hankali kan Asiya a Cibiyar Kula da Sabon Tsaron Amurka, wata kungiyar tunani.
Ministan harkokin wajen Syria ya ce Syria a shirye take ta karbi 'yan gudun hijirar da suka dawo.
Syria ta ce a shirye take da dawowar 'yan gudun hijirar da son rai, kuma tana neman taimako don sake gina kasar da ta shafe shekaru sama da bakwai tana fama da yakin basasa.
Da yake jawabi ga Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Waje Walid al-Ma'alam ya ce yanayin kasar na samun sauki.
"A yau, yanayin ƙasa ya fi karko da aminci saboda ci gaban da aka samu wajen yaƙar ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da sake farfado da yankunan da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata don dawo da al'amuran yau da kullun.
Yanzu duk yanayin da ake ciki don dawo da 'yan gudun hijirar da ke cikin kasar saboda ta'addanci da kuma matakan tattalin arziki na yau da kullum da ke fuskantar rayuwarsu da kuma rayuwa.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa 'yan Syria sama da miliyan 5.5 sun tsere daga kasar tun lokacin da yakin ya barke a 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida da ke zaune a kasar har yanzu suna bukatar taimakon jin kai.
Al-Maulom ya ce gwamnatin Syria za ta yi maraba da taimako wajen sake gina kasar da ta lalace.
Amma ya jaddada cewa ba zai yarda da taimako ko taimako daga kasashen da ke tallafawa tawaye ba.
Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a birnin Paris
Tawagar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder ta 2018 ta doke ta Amurka ta hanyar ci 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a wasan karshe a Le Golf National a wajen Paris, Faransa.
Yanzu Amurka ta sha kaye sau shida a jere a Turai kuma ba ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Lokacin da kyaftin din Denmark Thomas Jørn ya kai maki 14.5 da ake buƙata don doke Amurkawa, Turai ta sake lashe taken.
Tauraron Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya yi gwagwarmaya a gasar mafi girma, ya nuna T-shot a cikin ruwa a rami na 16 na Par 3 ta hanyar karɓar wasan daga Francesco Molinari.
Gwanin golf na Italiya Molinari ya ci nasara a duk zagaye na gasar, ya zama 1 daga cikin 'yan wasan 4 da suka ci 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a shekarar 1979.
Jordan Speith na Amurka ya sha kashi 5 da 4 daga Thorbjon Olesen na Denmark, dan wasan da ya fi karancin matsayi a kungiyar Turai.
Dan wasan da ya fi kowacce kasa daraja a duniya, Dustin Donson ya sha kashi 2 da 1 a hannun Lan Polter na Ingila, wanda watakila shi ne wasan karshe da ya buga a gasar Ryder Cup.
Wani tsohon dan wasan Ryder Cup guda takwas, dan kasar Spain Sergio Garcia ya zama dan Turai da ya lashe gasar a duk lokacin da ya samu maki 25.5.
"Ba na yawan kuka, amma a yau ba zan iya daina ba.
Wannan shekara ce mai wuya.
Don haka na gode Thomas don zabar ni da kuma amincewa da ni.
Na yi farin ciki sosai da na dawo da kofin.
Wannan game da kungiya ne, kuma ina matukar farin ciki da na taimaka", in ji Gracia cikin nutsuwa bayan nasarar Turai.
Ya ba da wutar ga abokin aikinsa John Ram, wanda ya doke almara na golf na Amurka Tiger Wood 2 da 1 a wasan daya a ranar Lahadi.
Rahm, mai shekara 23, ya ce, "Ina alfahari da yadda na doke Tiger Wood, na girma ina kallonsa".
Wood ya rasa dukkan wasanninsa hudu a Faransa kuma yanzu yana da rikodin Ryder Cup na 13-21-3.
Daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasa da suka taba lashe kofin duniya 14 a jere, na biyu kawai ga Jack Nichols.
Kungiyar Amurka ta yi gwagwarmaya a duk karshen mako don neman hanyar da ta dace, ban da Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Finney, waɗanda suka buga golf tare da cikakken ƙarfin a duk gasar.
