Sabuntawar Red Tide: Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota suna da ƙarancin taro
Rahoton labarai daga Hukumar Kifi da Daji ta Florida ya nuna cewa ana ganin raguwar yawan adadin Red Tide a wani bangare na yankin Tampa Bay.
A cewar FWC, an bayar da rahoton yanayin fashewar fashewar ruwa a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier Counties - wanda ke nuna cewa yawan taro ya ragu.
